 that our model can make effective recommendations of\nheterogeneous content.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2016 07:22:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2016 07:25:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2016 00:43:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-30"}
